string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Ino_2_idle_s
string.body: Hey! Please listen to what I've got to say.

string.name: STR_CHAT_LF1_Ino_3_idle_s
string.body: We have a big problem! Krall are plotting, plotting something.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_015_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, you know how to play.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_016_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, you are not leaving just like that.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_030_Die_S
string.body: Please avenge my death, my lord Saendukal...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_035_Batk_S
string.body: Today... shall be the day... you die...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_038_Katk_S
string.body: Leave... if you don't want to die...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_040_Die_S
string.body: I'd rather have an eternal rest...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_041_Batk_B
string.body: You will regret... having come here, [%userclass]...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_052_Katk_S
string.body: Kraark, I'll show you the power of magic!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_053_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, I will never forgive you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_060_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, it's been a while since I last tasted blood!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_065_Die_S
string.body: Grrrk, you are not bad at all...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_066_Die_S
string.body: Please avenge my death, my lord Saendukal...

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_071_Katk_S
string.body: Kraark, I'll give you a hot lesson!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_076_Batk_S
string.body: Kraark, how dare you come here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_078_Katk_S
string.body: You not so bad. Worthy opponent!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_084_Katk_S
string.body: Here, just take two more hits!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_085_Katk_S
string.body: Here, just take one more hit!

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_095_Batk_S
string.body: You don't seem to be afraid of me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_097_Die_S
string.body: It hurts, I don't want to die.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_098_Idle_S
string.body: I worked too long and I'm tired.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_099_Idle_S
string.body: I can't work, I'm too hungry.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_100_Batk_S
string.body: I'll hit you just a little.

string.name: STR_CHAT_E3_102_Atk_S

string.body: If your heart is burning, then perhaps you should see a healer.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_5
string.body: I've got to go. I need to... wash my wings. Or something.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_6
string.body: I'm not interested in wasting time with a man like you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_7
string.body: Bug off, lizard breath. I'm busy.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_9
string.body: Tenacity is a great quality, but I still think you're a pain in the neck.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_10
string.body: That's kind of you to say, but I'm not interested.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_11
string.body: What a sweet thing to say! I'll be sure to tell my boyfriend about it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_woman_ment_12
string.body: Oh, honey, I'm way out of your league!

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_idealist_ment_1
string.body: I dream of a world without war, where all can live in peace.

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_idealist_ment_2
string.body: There's so much suffering in the world. Shouldn't we strive to lessen it?

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_realist_ment_1
string.body: But can a world at peace have progress?

string.name: STR_CHAT_housing_realist_ment_2
string.body: Struggle and strife are a necessary part of life. Even animals fight between themselves!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF4b_Shugo_Spa_1
string.body: Ooh, lightheaded... maybe in hot spring for too long, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF4b_Shugo_Spa_2
string.body: Ooh, so hot! Feels so good!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF4b_Shugo_Spa_3
string.body: Come on in, Daeva. Water's fine, nyerk nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF4b_Shugo_Spa_4
string.body: Come on, get up! You can't spend all day in the bath, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_3_01_Idle_S
string.body: Onward! Be not afraid! I am right behind you, Kahrun!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_3_02_Idle_S
string.body: The Tiamat legion is still a force to be reckoned with! Keep your eyes open!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_4_01_Idle_S
string.body: How strange... I can't find the entrance to Tiamat's Hideout...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_4_02_Idle_S
string.body: The Tiamat Legion's downfall is nigh...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_6_01_Idle_S
string.body: The magic of the four Tiamat's Incarnations is preventing the passage from being activated. Please deal with them.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_1_01_Idle
string.body: Tiamat might have tracked us down by now. We must hurry.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_1_02_Idle
string.body: I've never seen such a strong Aetheric Field before.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_1_03_Idle
string.body: Today could be the day the Tiamat Legion meets its doom.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Surama_1_01_Idle_S
string.body: To receive help from a Daeva... I am truly ashamed.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Murugan_2_01_Idle_S
string.body: I'll open the door, but you must not disturb Surama!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Murugan_1_01
string.body: I never thought I'd be thanking a Daeva... I'm still alive thanks to you... Thank you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Murugan_1_03
string.body: Surama! I shall pave the way for you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Surama_2_03
string.body: Silence! Are you not ashamed to have gained your rank of Brigade General by treachery?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Surama_2_05
string.body: I never thought... that my life here... would come to an end... How very sad...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Rakshaka_01
string.body: Helped by a Daeva? The shame of it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Rakshaka_02
string.body: Perhaps it would be best to lock them up again, so that we have peace.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Rakshaka_03
string.body: What a weakling you are! So much for the mighty Surama!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Murugan_3_02
string.body: I can't believe it... Surama has been defeated...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Murugan_3_03
string.body: I thank you... for the revenge of Surama.

string.name: STR_QUEST_SAY_IDTiamat_02
string.body: You have my sincere thanks... Finally I am free again...

string.name: STR_QUEST_SAY_IDTiamat_03
string.body: You followed me all this way! Oh, you vile Elyos!

string.name: STR_QUEST_SAY_IDTiamat_06
string.body: Ah... Finally I am rid of my curse...

string.name: STR_QUEST_SAY_IDTiamat_07
string.body: I am most grateful for your help. Now I can relax...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_6_01
string.body: Very well. I shall take care of the final negotiation.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_ShulackScientist_01
string.body: There's no formula that I can't solve!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_ShulackScientist_02
string.body: More soil samples will be needed to research Poeta ...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_ShulackScientist_03
string.body: I don't know where the fourth volume of "The Forbidden Red Ocha" is...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kahrun_6_02
string.body: If you are ready, follow me.
